\Sexpr{nrow(empfullsos)} and EOS: $n =$
\Sexpr{nrow(empfulleos)}) or restricted datasets ($n =$ 
\Sexpr{nrow(emp)}; Figure \ref{fig:wcSOSEOScomparison}a). \\


